<collectingCountry id="F3157649EF00FFF749A41D9CFF1CFF24" box="[151,222,188,212]" name="China" pageId="1" pageNumber="63">China</collectingCountry>
. Recently, Francesco Vitali’s website on worldwide Cerambycoidea indicates that this genus also occurs in 
<collectingCountry id="F3157649EF00FFF749A41DFFFEC8FF07" box="[151,266,223,247]" name="Cambodia" pageId="1" pageNumber="63">Cambodia</collectingCountry>
(available from http://www.cerambycoidea.com/forum 
<number id="3DCA24FEEF00FFF74A4D1DFFFC49FF07" box="[894,907,223,247]" pageId="1" pageNumber="63" value="2.0">2</number>
.asp?id= 
<number id="3DCA24FEEF00FFF74AD01DFFFBDEFF07" box="[995,1052,223,247]" pageId="1" pageNumber="63" value="3844.0">3844</number>
, accessed 
<date id="FFBC1019EF00FFF74DA21DFFFA9EFF07" box="[1169,1372,223,247]" pageId="1" pageNumber="63" value="2012-02-20">
<number id="3DCA24FEEF00FFF74DA21DFFFB6FFF07" box="[1169,1197,223,247]" pageId="1" pageNumber="63" value="20.0">20</number>
February 
<number id="3DCA24FEEF00FFF74C2C1DFFFA9EFF07" box="[1311,1372,223,247]" pageId="1" pageNumber="63" value="2012.0">2012</number>
</date>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BBD36D9EF00FFF749FA1C25FCEDFE94" blockId="1.[151,1436,151,356]" pageId="1" pageNumber="63">
<taxonomicName id="4C024D5AEF00FFF749FA1C25FE72FEEC" authority="Pic" authorityName="Pic" box="[201,432,260,284]" class="Insecta" family="Cerambycidae" genus="Mimothestus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="63" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="annulicornis">
<emphasis id="B976EACBEF00FFF749FA1C25FE42FEEC" box="[201,384,260,284]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="63">M. annulicornis</emphasis>
